    <briefdescription>
<para>The beginnings of a service to track all background tasks. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This interface will eventually become a generic place to register long-running <ref refid="interfacesb_i_job_progress" kindref="compound">sbIJobProgress</ref> implementing tasks.</para><para>The idea is that Songbird may one day have a standardized task manager, looking something like <ulink url="http://dingo.songbirdnest.com/~komi/status-all-over/wireframes/service-pane-status-bar.png">http://dingo.songbirdnest.com/~komi/status-all-over/wireframes/service-pane-status-bar.png</ulink></para><para>Until this materializes all <ref refid="interfacesb_i_job_progress_service" kindref="compound">sbIJobProgressService</ref> can do is help launch a modal job progress dialog.</para><para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This interface is guaranteed to change </para></simplesect>
</para>    </detaileddescription>
